Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.47,0:24:32.76,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.76,0:24:34.99,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,An aerial lighthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.99,0:24:36.36,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dad, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.99,0:24:41.08,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
